<body>
    <h1>T8 -Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"35bb66d542ee" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"14b095993c5e" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h3>
<p local-id=3D"9503786881f4">This document defines the requirements for imp=
lementing a cloud-based PostgreSQL database system with full observability,=
 monitoring, analytics dashboards, and performance validation using AWS ser=
vices and Grafana Cloud.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d446ca2a64b5">The intended audience includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"197b4c3c13bf">
<li local-id=3D"aeaf0409ca17">
<p local-id=3D"4d4f7147f816">CTO (infrastructure validation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87f8de04abc5">
<p local-id=3D"acd8658ccdab">Solution Architect (design compliance)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"a348ac4ec074">
<p local-id=3D"76fa9b122afe">DevOps Engineers (deployment &amp; monitoring)=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd54c1bada6a">
<p local-id=3D"d8d605f195e2">Developers (performance validation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"061b6bdb334c">
<p local-id=3D"224687960b89">Operations Teams (incident analysis)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1465156508aa">This document serves as a blueprint for system=
 design before implementation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"5dffd42bb364">
<h3 local-id=3D"c82f4a3ddb53" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f6757be66966">In Scope</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aa8f6c89e412">
<li local-id=3D"5bbb830c1e2e">
<p local-id=3D"9e7f6e74c9a5">Provisioning Amazon RDS PostgreSQL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c616c20da8d">
<p local-id=3D"c991c838fb92">Configuring EC2 for workload simulation</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"1811d0d1eb0a">
<p local-id=3D"23f3ffc5a42a">Importing structured dataset from SQLite to Po=
stgreSQL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fad85de8d4db">
<p local-id=3D"b450116de74d">Integrating CloudWatch metrics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f202d7668ce">
<p local-id=3D"92f321b3a1f8">Enabling RDS Performance Insights</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e188032864e1">
<p local-id=3D"3e9c3e4e6be9">Creating Grafana Infrastructure Dashboard</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"6e8ae0207576">
<p local-id=3D"105672570ca2">Creating Grafana Analytics Dashboard</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1af5be707ac">
<p local-id=3D"b168b8f4ed49">Implementing automated load simulation</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"5f36b3b02a92">
<p local-id=3D"690fe02b39a2">Monitoring DBLoad behavior under workload</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"90b371a7f728">Out of Scope</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c3186da2029b">
<li local-id=3D"9656e033a702">
<p local-id=3D"3a8515a0d601">Multi-region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2629ad21399">
<p local-id=3D"97463450f329">Multi-AZ high availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bca23b1c07b2">
<p local-id=3D"1fe57473b2ca">Production-grade CI/CD pipelines</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a32c14c9fa5d">
<p local-id=3D"f39b7c8cf8a1">Enterprise-level security hardening</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1e16b9001e4">
<p local-id=3D"a1ba760f2f44">Full Infrastructure as Code automation</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8801d2e3cd46">
<h3 local-id=3D"bcda5a6fe5d1" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.3Defin=
itions,Acronyms,andAbbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviati=
ons</h3>
<h3 local-id=3D"62c089bb90df" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=E2=80=
=93RelationalDatabaseServiceEC2=E2=80=93ElasRDSticComputeCloudDBLoad=E2=80=
=93DatabaseLoad(AverageActiveSessions)IOPS=E2=80=93Input/OutputOperationsPe=
rSecondAWS=E2=80=93AmazonWebServicesPI=E2=80=93PerformanceInsightsIaC=E2=80=
=93InfrastructureasCodeSG=E2=80=93SecurityGroup">=E2=80=93 Relational Datab=
ase Service<br>
EC2 =E2=80=93 ElasRDS tic Compute Cloud<br>
DBLoad =E2=80=93 Database Load (Average Active Sessions)<br>
IOPS =E2=80=93 Input/Output Operations Per Second<br>
AWS =E2=80=93 Amazon Web Services<br>
PI =E2=80=93 Performance Insights<br>
IaC =E2=80=93 Infrastructure as Code<br>
SG =E2=80=93 Security Group</h3>
<hr local-id=3D"984cd4f1d392">
<h3 local-id=3D"67a9ee4d4b4a" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.4Refer=
ences">1.4 References</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3a9b4205a438">
<li local-id=3D"b314f48f2c13">
<p local-id=3D"ba58522d7c68">AWS RDS Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d18ed1fc558f">
<p local-id=3D"167a7c7e86c6">AWS EC2 Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8e9120fcc36">
<p local-id=3D"5f8ddf4d949f">AWS CloudWatch Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6492dff24f47">
<p local-id=3D"3e2752031440">AWS Well-Architected Framework</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7a3883b1680">
<p local-id=3D"d06ba9450143">Grafana Cloud Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea19880f801c">
<p local-id=3D"608080a8195a">RDS Performance Insights Documentation</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e446348ea4ae">
<h3 local-id=3D"cd3c9d159a72" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h3>
<p local-id=3D"fbcdac3d8f72">This document describes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dde07027e116">
<li local-id=3D"e1608f3a2e47">
<p local-id=3D"c0bb47d53b66">Project objectives</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4573ddfe3972">
<p local-id=3D"989cb2db41eb">Business goals</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"216be34f85cf">
<p local-id=3D"91a1b11f202d">Functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8e8e8a08465">
<p local-id=3D"47d5416ac224">Non-functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e387ed6359c9">
<p local-id=3D"65a6c4244c36">Constraints and assumptions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d0c37115ec5">
<p local-id=3D"d93b484da6a0">Risk analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92058dd5b399">
<p local-id=3D"ff3b4d5fe5f8">Security and compliance expectations</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"77b0b7ea18f8">
<h1 local-id=3D"46bd7585ee2f" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"31f823d8aa49" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h3>
<p local-id=3D"210d0d450773">The primary objectives are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d7c40e8dc8a1">
<li local-id=3D"3ada2648c870">
<p local-id=3D"8c40959cbba5">Deploy a managed PostgreSQL database in AWS</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"272a7e896571">
<p local-id=3D"93f8e5038d1e">Import structured dataset into RDS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13ae771dc67b">
<p local-id=3D"1bfe4dc44a04">Enable infrastructure-level monitoring</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"5338627588ea">
<p local-id=3D"d1720c5df094">Build SQL-based analytics dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7afe7c337e98">
<p local-id=3D"1cc5279adbd8">Simulate database load</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ce7e9cecf78">
<p local-id=3D"81fad59906fa">Validate system performance under stress</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"554ed5d5db43">
<p local-id=3D"0f9d23b8a48d">Analyze database behavior using Performance In=
sights</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"17b0b2038013">
<h3 local-id=3D"b7d446a0eaa6" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"90651598affb">
<li local-id=3D"fbb65e2e4f30">
<p local-id=3D"00ef748b7871">Improve infrastructure observability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afd2f1320f7e">
<p local-id=3D"0e4a90df432e">Reduce database performance risks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"326d3a93f382">
<p local-id=3D"c14490f1d0bd">Enable real-time visibility into DB health</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"52e1ff654c5f">
<p local-id=3D"72ec5a135798">Provide performance validation before producti=
on deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"07855ca923c5">
<p local-id=3D"33f7c6ba69f2">Prevent downtime caused by undetected DB bottl=
enecks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15204f73e21f">
<p local-id=3D"8a4672943263">Establish DevOps best practices alignment</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b7786717b6d4">
<h3 local-id=3D"bb4d5620b205" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1996ca1434bc">Traditional database deployments lack:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"42d7b9d1ff2c">
<li local-id=3D"42629677013e">
<p local-id=3D"b8614a8409a1">Real-time infrastructure visibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9675db76732">
<p local-id=3D"fbd06424fa8f">Performance load validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ec75655bbe39">
<p local-id=3D"3889214a8102">Centralized dashboarding</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d05c1d5ee61">
<p local-id=3D"35beb1ae11b0">Observability integration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1d9a0fa32348">The system aims to demonstrate a cloud-native =
monitored database aligned with AWS Well-Architected Framework principles.<=
/p>
<hr local-id=3D"bc2f55038836">
<h3 local-id=3D"faa13c784505" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"796d7442d41d">
<li local-id=3D"1d3af2ea9491">
<p local-id=3D"ca1ed0bc2d44">Free-tier compatible architecture (db.t3.micro=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa33fd8544e1">
<p local-id=3D"0f0931dc49ee">Single-region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93db848c7015">
<p local-id=3D"5b690c31db22">Limited budget</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e19e5e65f2c">
<p local-id=3D"662d66800d64">Manual provisioning via AWS Console</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a900e6d2f93e">
<p local-id=3D"01fd4890396f">Execution timeline limited to same-day deliver=
y</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7032a764accb">
<p local-id=3D"1c6a7220f5ce">Public access temporarily enabled for demo (no=
t production safe)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1787970764ba">
<h1 local-id=3D"bdf8a0f113fa" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"e2ffb6f8b665" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e86cad1e03c9">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f28c3b021537">
<li local-id=3D"211cb3fc6522">
<p local-id=3D"0c1c6b2aed34">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b393321c454c">
<p local-id=3D"bfb2e4553f94">EC2 Instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39400a288fe7">
<p local-id=3D"84d8893f2fa6">Amazon RDS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1248bc33ceea">
<p local-id=3D"29fc98fcc60c">CloudWatch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"82b4d8729544">
<p local-id=3D"ea6343beadac">Grafana Cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b628888ae079">
<p local-id=3D"9bbea2c9a947">Performance Insights</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260309-184509.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"9bf8d315ca3d3dd4b79856e094e65a961298ff243d2f77a2ebaa5487111648a8" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/181=
6592404/image-20260309-184509.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D177308=
1911911&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"822" data-width=
=3D"1071" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"18=
45231697" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"a=
ttachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260309-184509.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
ontent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1816592404" =
data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"61fe4574-4bfc=
-4304-bc92-e19496f73763" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"358"></span>
<p local-id=3D"4e97187d08dd"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"6b0b054e6c05">
<h3 local-id=3D"7a0b8891b73e" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h3>
<hr local-id=3D"bf3a57236316">
<h3 local-id=3D"79a85959ce3a" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:ProvisionRDSPostgreSQL">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Provision RDS PostgreSQL</h=
3>
<p local-id=3D"293b4a62a8f8">Description:<br>
System must allow provisioning of PostgreSQL database instance in AWS.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cc55392f1305">Actors:<br>
DevOps Engineer, AWS Console</p>
<p local-id=3D"a5bddaa6e17d">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"319e27be517e">
<li local-id=3D"c1d02ccebf8f">
<p local-id=3D"f195c0d36ca4">AWS account available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c2d89b2dc14">
<p local-id=3D"91ae3590ca9d">Required permissions assigned</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f2c166309599">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"72e7067e260b">
<li local-id=3D"d539d868ba58">
<p local-id=3D"508e7859c621">RDS instance created and available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b077dcc44af9">Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"63cedbfd151d">
<li local-id=3D"60524bf2c9f9">
<p local-id=3D"ff4499f92cfe">Create RDS PostgreSQL instance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9496e267fbe5">
<p local-id=3D"eb7f52c8989e">Configure storage and instance class.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"efde2ccf1a6a">
<p local-id=3D"71fff117526e">Configure networking and security group.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"8d7f2f0d9d4b">
<p local-id=3D"bc0f10d966e4">Enable monitoring features.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"12dfe5798d4a">Alternative Flow:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"74f68ca8c37d">
<li local-id=3D"9377df90b70f">
<p local-id=3D"753b485690b6">Incorrect security group =E2=86=92 connection =
failure.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c211c5b0e38">
<p local-id=3D"dd69f9fd2a6e">Storage misconfiguration =E2=86=92 performance=
 degradation.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"afdeae772c88">
<h3 local-id=3D"0283f997362e" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:ImportDataset">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Import Dataset</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3eedc635e7df">Description:<br>
System must support importing structured SQLite dataset into PostgreSQL.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"84d82462024b">Actors:<br>
DevOps Engineer, EC2, RDS</p>
<p local-id=3D"998597328341">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1e6d97246a06">
<li local-id=3D"ec4adb6ebe69">
<p local-id=3D"28f602e7555b">Dataset files available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73b949c6e877">
<p local-id=3D"b75986054009">RDS reachable from EC2</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"efe1ec934430">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d07c412984a1">
<li local-id=3D"ea9d0a53c4a6">
<p local-id=3D"86680952771b">Tables created in PostgreSQL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bfaa7a2dbc5">
<p local-id=3D"93314236326d">Data validated via row counts</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ad0795ba2997">Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6209c64cbf12">
<li local-id=3D"e79c4fbe64e1">
<p local-id=3D"d0b0c6313928">Convert SQLite schema.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e0fdad48e08">
<p local-id=3D"ecd8982f1275">Import data into PostgreSQL.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29433cdd1f3e">
<p local-id=3D"3b0e32a5f9ca">Validate table creation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58325f0c94c3">
<p local-id=3D"dde943374690">Validate record counts.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"cadf59257fbc">Alternative Flow:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e00e60ac9e82">
<li local-id=3D"c88318b6f84e">
<p local-id=3D"8ed5a55eac94">Schema mismatch =E2=86=92 import failure.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"e4d8c7038144">
<p local-id=3D"68cc71ea02c0">Connection issue =E2=86=92 retry required.</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8f4365e01fac">
<h3 local-id=3D"4687c1c98b6e" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.3Use=
Case3:MonitorInfrastructureMetrics">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Monitor Infrastructur=
e Metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"253f0e430b7b">Description:<br>
System must collect and display infrastructure metrics.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a6247108db8a">Actors:<br>
RDS, CloudWatch, Grafana</p>
<p local-id=3D"7ee090c5cb70">Metrics Required:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"82ffb53e58b9">
<li local-id=3D"6b3e11ff505d">
<p local-id=3D"9f369aeed943">CPUUtilization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19f15bb02331">
<p local-id=3D"076de26ea20d">FreeableMemory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1b69adee187">
<p local-id=3D"1f6119778e8c">FreeStorageSpace</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"910e003b7adb">
<p local-id=3D"e523eb7b551e">DatabaseConnections</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f31f0bb22b37">
<p local-id=3D"89192828937d">ReadIOPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55f44ee84435">
<p local-id=3D"7919863e5865">WriteIOPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc0687216bfc">
<p local-id=3D"ab60deae7e12">DBLoad</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7c912c102fe">
<p local-id=3D"7103fb8d5d14">DBLoadCPU</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99e8a8e4f19c">
<p local-id=3D"47b4ec868f53">DBLoadNonCPU</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f8f5e648d678">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6e7bb5ee1f0c">
<li local-id=3D"2a8bdee4fb77">
<p local-id=3D"fc170b5c9adf">Metrics visible in Grafana dashboard.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6e614b444f3b">
<h3 local-id=3D"8c6d2ff31232" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.4Use=
Case4:PerformLoadSimulation">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Perform Load Simulation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"25c583c1dd9a">Description:<br>
System must simulate database load using automated script.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0dd8ac41d404">Actors:<br>
EC2, PostgreSQL</p>
<p local-id=3D"0b33ea7d5478">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ebea078d4595">
<li local-id=3D"7ab138f52110">
<p local-id=3D"3b09b072324a">Python script deployed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"607457132c9d">
<p local-id=3D"4adc76b13d9c">Cron job configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"705026d1328c">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"05ec14b75e5d">
<li local-id=3D"f5f63aaa9654">
<p local-id=3D"395870f2e3db">Queries executed repeatedly</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13448e488470">
<p local-id=3D"1e50f6460013">DBLoad increased under stress</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1a68dfee0b84">Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"64ebe4c82edc">
<li local-id=3D"1e0129e6c187">
<p local-id=3D"7ee9c65ca693">Script connects to database.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae5c8a67758a">
<p local-id=3D"de91f6df74e6">Random queries executed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4cf9e26ca0e">
<p local-id=3D"ef58d68e9bd1">Transactions committed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e5702cca07f">
<p local-id=3D"caa0d56f2592">Script runs periodically via cron.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c01afdf1f374">Alternative Flow:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd571bb2eca0">
<li local-id=3D"b64fb9c4e5ea">
<p local-id=3D"26c4b4404cf1">DB connection failure =E2=86=92 log error.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"4da80b8606e9">
<p local-id=3D"1d3664d3640e">Sequential execution insufficient =E2=86=92 pa=
rallelization required.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b9d8d3551332">
<h3 local-id=3D"a622f7ce9a8a" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.5Use=
Case5:AnalyzePerformance">3.2.5 Use Case 5: Analyze Performance</h3>
<p local-id=3D"453861a1bee3">Description:<br>
System must allow root cause analysis using Performance Insights.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8e0ba6f4a449">Actors:<br>
DevOps Engineer, Performance Insights</p>
<p local-id=3D"0d4ea2ca430b">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"883e80765c21">
<li local-id=3D"e590dcf5cc31">
<p local-id=3D"0999997c773f">Query-level analysis available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cccd975162b8">
<p local-id=3D"c78583b45b3e">CPU vs IO load differentiation possible</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d7c9fd897bcc">
<h3 local-id=3D"5f5e1b2e8440" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.6Use=
Case6:BuildAnalyticsDashboard">3.2.6 Use Case 6: Build Analytics Dashboard<=
/h3>
<p local-id=3D"7fe621ba4ea7">Description:<br>
System must display SQL analytics data.</p>
<p local-id=3D"eef829856369">Dashboard Components:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"415625d55061">
<li local-id=3D"34e3917898e6">
<p local-id=3D"5c0ff84ff745">Total Cities</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4190204f1ec2">
<p local-id=3D"dca4c13e7e1e">Top 10 Countries</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85f1c45fbc68">
<p local-id=3D"46db22a9d255">Population Metrics</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b4a091ea33b4">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"533b3688b0d7">
<li local-id=3D"290d37e7546b">
<p local-id=3D"e23126faa949">Dataset successfully imported</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e7a8aae67789">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"74713e825bb3">
<li local-id=3D"cf95b9398930">
<p local-id=3D"a11ff543adf5">Real-time analytics visible in Grafana.</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2e449358c047">
<h1 local-id=3D"75faa731746a" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"6ae97e7fe756" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c71477ca17c1">
<li local-id=3D"faf769014021">
<p local-id=3D"85335fcf4702">Database must support simulated concurrent wor=
kload.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa0e7acf2e6e">
<p local-id=3D"ccdfd6324b4c">Monitoring refresh interval =E2=89=A4 1 minute=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee7c806b6c95">
<p local-id=3D"c35a273222a2">Load simulation must generate measurable DBLoa=
d.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af96d4b735a4">
<p local-id=3D"3cf18e194178">Instance must remain stable under load.</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"65f32e6b3460">
<h3 local-id=3D"25cb1ed4675d" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0ceda4294995">
<li local-id=3D"b0758cedfd86">
<p local-id=3D"c0cb33bb934f">Database encryption enabled.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83fd2690c6c6">
<p local-id=3D"99af28027c3f">Security groups restrict DB port.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f3a836c49bbc">
<p local-id=3D"807acd668e58">SSH key-based authentication only.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64c894ce5ae8">
<p local-id=3D"1eac03998942">No hardcoded credentials in production.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"7637ed20de0d">
<p local-id=3D"3354a13b1baa">Use AWS Secrets Manager (recommended).</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"d1f2361662e8">
<p local-id=3D"9451992427eb">Database should not be publicly accessible in =
production.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0eddc7ef80b9">
<h3 local-id=3D"dd328c136e5c" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bc9f081297bc">
<li local-id=3D"37461ca8af06">
<p local-id=3D"41816de23c89">Dashboards must clearly display infrastructure=
 and analytics.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a78193e23a06">
<p local-id=3D"a6c3b367a775">Performance metrics must be visually distingui=
shable.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2ef2579609f">
<p local-id=3D"9665f72c9254">DBLoad graph must clearly reflect load changes=
.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"04f20e1ab710">
<h3 local-id=3D"5cc27fd791b3" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"9152c7b747f1">
<li local-id=3D"d55f3354e0a8">
<p local-id=3D"9f2f27b0d4db">RDS managed backups enabled.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"faac0021a02c">
<p local-id=3D"830dcf027615">Storage autoscaling supported.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2d6cc2fa48c1">
<p local-id=3D"97d40b4c5bc7">Monitoring must continue even during workload =
spikes.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff77cfe0a41f">
<p local-id=3D"49d791a0b548">CloudWatch integration must remain consistent.=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d3e52a8caca6">
<h3 local-id=3D"4d553223cefd" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.5Compl=
ianceRequirements">4.5 Compliance Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e08623e340ef">
<li local-id=3D"80098fe15153">
<p local-id=3D"c7584339cfb9">Align with AWS Well-Architected Framework.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7da0506dd6c6">
<p local-id=3D"3e993c41da10">Follow least-privilege IAM principle.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5ff8ce6cb2b">
<p local-id=3D"6d030de04ec5">Avoid public database exposure.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd9a7e886127">
<p local-id=3D"02f5a1a02f5b">Encrypt performance monitoring data.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cd7f01da7f81">
<h1 local-id=3D"d06b8f41af84" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"59544787633e" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.1Assum=
ptions">5.1 Assumptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a5371db43f6f">
<li local-id=3D"c64d1471264f">
<p local-id=3D"f15558dc6cd8">AWS account available.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f7fbdc74d24">
<p local-id=3D"359c5a7c47ed">Grafana Cloud account available.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"66cc85ed7ccc">
<p local-id=3D"aa4d45a642a7">Internet connectivity available.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eacc4f374506">
<p local-id=3D"b1f8076c261f">Dataset files are valid and complete.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"452b0ab73f6f">
<p local-id=3D"7df489193d65">User has AWS Console access.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ad85d91faa2e">
<h3 local-id=3D"d75a4fb1067f" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.2Depen=
dencies">5.2 Dependencies</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"88e121d6d923">
<li local-id=3D"38816b666ea5">
<p local-id=3D"a7e6a067ff75">Amazon RDS PostgreSQL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a0f0956bac3">
<p local-id=3D"e74861c53be3">Amazon EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7a2ee608d8a">
<p local-id=3D"bbf8d89c9844">Amazon CloudWatch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bad4ef02efaa">
<p local-id=3D"e7f0c398620a">Grafana Cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e9bea1984df">
<p local-id=3D"81fe0cadd64b">AWS Performance Insights</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b3435bcc40a9">
<p local-id=3D"bbeb36427e4c">Python runtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f63790c7d41">
<p local-id=3D"3abc1a67cffd">Cron scheduler</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a2c0b6ac57cb">
<h1 local-id=3D"1879f4bd514b" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"eff78f257f3a" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.1RiskI=
dentification">6.1 Risk Identification</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0c0f09e074ce">
<li local-id=3D"271242efaf41">
<p local-id=3D"e6231b010ede">Public database exposure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"987a014217ad">
<p local-id=3D"8eed8fbfd4e7">Insufficient load simulation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"41ab43b44d15">
<p local-id=3D"fe76d69057fd">Misconfigured security groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"42a5ae8aacaf">
<p local-id=3D"906aa37d8c87">IAM misconfiguration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9877c30ea70f">
<p local-id=3D"f7cb3ac00df8">DB instance resource exhaustion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"07ebc1f15c92">
<p local-id=3D"6e9f08f1a751">Cost overrun</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8e08a5d60f11">
<h3 local-id=3D"65978e6bc9a4" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.2RiskM=
itigation">6.2 Risk Mitigation</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"cd28c5d467a6">
<li local-id=3D"3f251269af08">
<p local-id=3D"95cdebd82b06">Restrict database access to private subnet.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"2af62ac674b1">
<p local-id=3D"171928bcc545">Implement concurrent load testing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37003478cbcc">
<p local-id=3D"9044f863c196">Follow least privilege IAM.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cba4d8dbd28a">
<p local-id=3D"f832a5ae44ed">Monitor DBLoad continuously.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11aff4265174">
<p local-id=3D"11804391fe79">Right-size instance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"191c43c55662">
<p local-id=3D"2d4d714664ce">Track AWS billing.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4dba5c838edc">
<h1 local-id=3D"80764b086b46" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c2cc2901a929">Observability =E2=80=93 Ability to measure int=
ernal state from outputs<br>
DBLoad =E2=80=93 Average active database sessions<br>
IOPS =E2=80=93 Disk operation rate<br>
Infrastructure Monitoring =E2=80=93 System-level metric tracking<br>
Analytics Dashboard =E2=80=93 SQL-driven business insights</p>
<hr local-id=3D"5d6c8807d2cf">
<h1 local-id=3D"7e3546b7d9f7" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-8.Append=
ices">8. Appendices</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"5b2a6bdcc103">
<li local-id=3D"be063d9429c0">
<p local-id=3D"c647f1a5285f">Architecture Diagram</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bd554d9662a6">
<p local-id=3D"7620829d4fbb">Dashboard Screenshots</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2acaf9067cf4">
<p local-id=3D"3810073b42fc">Performance Insights Screenshots</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"281accbaebd7">
<p local-id=3D"45f14cfa7f8a">Cron Configuration Screenshot</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e14ea0d3fa72">
<p local-id=3D"52e672e865f8">Dataset Validation Evidence</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c535237844c0">
<h1 local-id=3D"24a3398f8643" id=3D"T8-RequirementAnalysisDocument-9.Custom=
erAcknowledgement">9. Customer Acknowledgement</h1>
